Review System
1. User can add rating (0-5) to a product
2. Text based review for same rating
3. Like the Review
4. API for top 10 review based on likes for product;

Expectation
   data model
   api
   classes / entity


Entities
1. User
2. Product
3. Review
4. Like

DataModels
1.User
    id
    name
    emailId
    createAt
    updatedAt

2.Product
    id
    name
    category
    price
    createAt
    updatedAt

3.Review
    id
    text :
    rating
    user_id
    product_id
    createAt
    updatedAt

4.Like
    id
    user_id
    review_id
    createAt
    updatedAt

select r.productId , l.reviewId , count(l.userId) from Like l , Review r
    where l.reviewId = r.id and r.productid = XYZ
    group by r.productId,l.reviewId order count(l.userId) desc limit k;
5. ReviewLike
    id
    reviewId
    count


API
    User
    1.create (name,email)
    2.update (id , name , email)
    3.read (id)
    3.delete (id)


